reviewText: It did not help me make the grade.
Some of the information in these videos is silly but overall, very helpful.  I would recommend for use in middle-high school classes.
This product was bought and sent to another person and there has been no feedback.  I do think that it will be helpful.

the humor is dorky but i tell my Academic Writing students to disregard it and pay attention to the content; it works and makes lessons lively and to a certain degree entertaining due to the silliness of the jokes, heh.
This is a quality DVD, but I would recommend using online videos that will give you the same information for free. Nothing bad about it, but nothing spectacular either.

Great tool to have before a serious writing project.
Especially if you have not written serious projects in many years.
Video was a must for my classes. Students really enjoyed watching and learning from this video. I would highly recommend it for any class that has English.
